Program: Outlook
Title: 9/11 Interviews
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsk6
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Interviews with survivors and people associated with the regeneration of Ground Zero in New York five years after 9/11. A memorable journey to Iran by an 11 year old girl from Berlin. Former Robben Island prisoner Sedick Isaacs and his work in education for students with problems. Finally, the Ukranian who was imprisoned in Siberia for raising the Ukranian flag. Show less